snippet.title: Recall: Empty Wishes - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Dive into the creepy world of Recall: Empty Wishes in this trailer for the upcoming psychological thriller horror game based in Taiwan in the 2010s. Recall: Empty Wishes will be coming to PC.

Ever since Tommy's disappearance, his sister Yonny has been searching for him. One day, she finds a toy phone that connects her and her friend to a world constructed of past memories, allowing them to delve into the private thoughts of others and uncover the truth surrounding Tommy's disappearance.

#gametrailers #gaming
